no 1 opposition party tripled their strength to 36 
of the 126 seats being contested in the 252seat upper house the 
liberal democrats hold 66 the socialists 22 the komeito clean 
government party 12 the communists eight minor parties 13 and 
independents five 
before takeshitas resignation three cabinet ministers were 
forced to step down due to links to the recruit co a publishing 
conglomerate that allegedly doled out millions of dollars in 
political donations and underpriced stock shares in exchange for 
favors 
