gorbachev making a threeday visit to france with his wife 
raisa recalled dealing with bushs predecessor ronald reagan 
when attempts were made to give us lessons to make 
prosecutorialtype accusations against us 
the idea is not to score propaganda points but to really 
understand that we are coming out of a complex period of cold war 
encumbered with mistrust confrontation and all of this has to be 
gotten rid of for this we have to be very wise and very 
courageous the soviet president said 
