lond0n ap prime minister margaret thatcher swapped her 
limousine for a river launch and two royal parks were turned into 
emergency parking lots after rail and bus workers went on strike 
wednesday for the third time in three weeks 
troops laid metal sheets on park lawns to protect the grass even 
